c: 31
v: 34
t: Ndithudi Mulungu ndiye yekha amene amadziwa za kudza kwake kwa tsiku lachiweruzo. Ndiye amene amatsitsa mvula ndiponso amadziwa zimene zili m’mimba mwa akazi. Ndipo palibe amene amadziwa zimene zingamuonekere mawa ndipo palibe amene amadziwa dziko limene adzafere. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi Wodziwa ndi Wozindikira